  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\nMigration fails when custom `contracts_build_directory` set in `truffle.js`\r\nIssue already raised in [truffle-migrate project](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle-migrate/issues/10) but those issues might not be monitored\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. set a non standard build directory in truffle.js (eg: `contracts_build_directory: './src/contractsBuild'`)\r\n1. run `truffle migrate`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nBuild should output to the directory `contracts_build_directory` set in `truffle.js`\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n```\r\n$ truffle migrate\r\nUsing network 'development'.\r\n\r\nRunning migration: 1_initial_migration.js\r\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:49072\r\n  throw new Error(\"Could not find artifacts for \" + import_path + \" from any sources\");\r\n  ^\r\n\r\nError: Could not find artifacts for ./Migrations.sol from any sources\r\n    at Resolver.require (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:49072:9)\r\n    at Object.require (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:66980:36)\r\n    at ResolverIntercept.require (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:219957:32)\r\n    at /Users/petro/ether/ucd-poc/migrations/1_initial_migration.js:1:28\r\n    at ContextifyScript.Script.runInContext (vm.js:53:29)\r\n    at ContextifyScript.Script.runInNewContext (vm.js:59:15)\r\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:96391:14\r\n    at tryToString (fs.js:513:3)\r\n    at FSReqWrap.readFileAfterClose [as oncomplete] (fs.js:501:12)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: MacOs Sierra 10.12.6\r\n* Truffle version: 3.4.9\r\n* Ethereum client: N/A (using TestRPC 4.0.1) \r\n* node version: 8.2.1\r\n* npm version:  5.3.0\r\n",
